{"tid":1395854,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候屌醒以為移民就無事嗰班中產！","createTime":"2019-08-02T01:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T03:45:55.000Z","uid":262035,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1c16268da3d121fcf23ffe842c42fe056d06ba89","tid":1395854,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:45:03.000Z","msg":"好心你地班投機主義既中產唔好咁天真<br />\n以為場仗輸左之後搞移民就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">場仗輸左你地隨時民都移唔到<br />\n留係香港共享大灣區榮耀同社會信用制度</span></span><br />\n<br />\n移民從來都係睇<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">專業技能</span></span>或者<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">資產</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果你無任何<span style=\"color: red;\">專業資格</span>，又或者年紀唔輕<br />\n特別係大公司啲中層管理者<br />\n唔好意思！靠專才移民條路你已經行唔到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為啲外國公司無謂請個年紀大、無專業資格又唔熟當地市場同文化既人做野，係佢地眼中自己國內都已經有大量人材可以用，點解要請個外國黎而充滿不確定性既人黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">但你自問自己有充足<span style=\"color: red;\">資產</span>移民既話<br />\n又不妨諗下去到移個陣仲有幾多剩</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年六四後香港大概有三十萬人移民<br />\n但當時仲有唔少人傻閪咁<br />\n相信一國兩制同五十年不變而無走<br />\n<br />\n去到今日已經無人相信一國兩制五十年不變<br />\n大灣區融合已經事在必行<br />\n社會信用制度既硬件已經裝置緊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港好快就變到同大陸無分別<br />\n到時有過半香港人搞移民都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n（每次投票都有6成人投泛民）<br />\n<br />\n當大家都諗住移民，樓市需求下跌供應上升<br />\n你層樓個樓價就凍過水，仲唔好提層樓未供完<br />\n你手上啲港元資產都因為唔少轉移資金而跌<br />\n而家又咁岩踩正香港既十年經濟周期<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你手上啲資產好快就貶值到唔夠你移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲未提外國見到咁多人移民會收緊審查</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人人都以為自己係移到民個兩成<br />\n但無諗過自己係剩返個八成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">所以咪諗住會獨善其身<br />\n繼續返工同睇直播就算<br />\n<br />\n若果呢場運動輸左<br />\n班中產會輸得最甘<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">所以8.5罷工約定你</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"8c1cbef1d581915554697e1134a2d56b189fefa9","tid":1395854,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"乜連登仔唔係個個都月入5萬、住私樓嫁咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec819dfc3eb4c0eba7bb7739570c4adf58dec2b6","tid":1395854,"uid":232466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:57:37.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d094257f54a0c770e20acb2fe5af645dde57f92c","tid":1395854,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:05:20.000Z","msg":"8月5 大罷工"},{"pid":"13bc2aabb56610c2bc2b52eb9e5c96fe5d06867b","tid":1395854,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:49:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f13e7c29ccfed6fbc83e0b5437cd17d292d0fd7","tid":1395854,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:18:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6670044500cfc75d102dc2c2dda0a2ddc624962","tid":1395854,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c16268da3d121fcf23ffe842c42fe056d06ba89","tid":1395854,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:45:03.000Z","msg":"好心你地班投機主義既中產唔好咁天真<br />\n以為場仗輸左之後搞移民就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-siz